  <brief_title>Limited Compression Ultrasound by Emergency Physicians to Exclude Deep Vein Thrombosis</brief_title>
  <official_title>Can Emergency Physicians Safely Exclude Proximal Deep Vein Thrombosis Using Limited Compression Emergency Department Ultrasound?</official_title>
